	<h1 class="title">「票房」《银河护卫队》大捷，但好莱坞并非不可战胜</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/73/small/73.jpg?1415670876" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">俞斯译</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-10-14 09:04:33 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/2831/medium/2831.jpg?1436654924" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="2831" data-title="《「票房」《银河护卫队》大捷，但好莱坞并非不可战胜》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/2831/medium/2831.jpg?1436654924" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/2831.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
